{
  "texts": [
    "Human oversight is necessary to interpret the data and results produced by AI.",
    "Additionally, an independent group should assess the impact of AI on research outcomes and ethical issues.",
    "Lastly, attention must be paid to the energy consumption of AI systems and their consequent carbon footprint, which can be considerable, especially in the case of large-scale computational models [32].",
    "AI and machine learning models, particularly those utilizing deep learning, require extensive computational resources and use significant amounts of electricity.",
    "To minimize this footprint, researchers should focus on optimizing AI algorithms to increase their energy efficiency and employ these systems only when absolutely necessary."
  ]
}